Finally, we just have to run our **Behavior Tree** with a single node.

## Steps

1. Create a **Run Behavior Tree** node.

	![](rbtNode.png)

1. Set the BTAsset value to the **Behavior Tree** asset you created in step 3.

	![](runBTsetBT.png)

1. Connect the output execution pin of the **Set Value as Vector** node to the input execution pin of the **Run Behavior Tree** node.

	[REGION:lightbox]
	[![](fullEG.png)(w:920 convert:false)](fullEG.png)
	[/REGION]
	
1. Save your AI Controller Blueprint.


